    <item>
      <title>英伟达在 CES 上展示全新 AI 产品，亚洲芯片股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/asia-chip-shares-surge-ahead-of-nvidia-ceo-s-vegas-appearance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于英伟达公司首席执行官黄仁勋在拉斯维加斯举行的 CES 贸易展上发布了采用该公司 Blackwell 芯片的新产品，重新点燃了人们对人工智能需求的乐观情绪，亚洲芯片相关股票延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/asia-chip-shares-surge-ahead-of-nvidia-ceo-s-vegas-appearance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 02:21:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
